data.description: **Showings will begin Monday 4/8/24** Stunning Front Porch Views of Mt. Yonah!  This generously sized open & bright floor plan features 3 Bedrooms + bonus room, & 2.5 baths.  The Primary Suite is located on the main level with a walk-in closet, double vanity, large soaking tub & separate shower.  Conveniently located just off of the garage on the main level, you'll find a large laundry room and separate access stairs to the upper-level bonus room.  With large gatherings in mind, from the kitchen to the outdoor yard, there's an abundant amount of space to enjoy time with friends and family.  With some TLC, you can make this house your home and enjoy the gorgeous surrounding mountain views. Utilities to Note: Trailwave High Speed Fiberoptic Internet, Cleveland City Water, HEMC Power, Propane Fireplace, Septic tank & lines are located in front yard, well on property is not in use.
